<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>


<div>
    <h3>1. What is Calm&Connect?</h3>
    <p>Calm&Connect is a platform that connects users to anonymous psychiatric consultancy services.</p>

    <h3>2. How do I book an appointment?</h3>
    <p>You can book an appointment by visiting the "Appointments" section and selecting either "Anonymous", "Online", or "Offline" options.</p>

    <h3>3. Are the consultations anonymous?</h3>
    <p>Yes, all consultations on Calm&Connect are completely anonymous. Your identity and personal information will be kept confidential.</p>

    <h3>4. How much does a consultation cost?</h3>
    <p>The cost of the consultation depends on the type (Anonymous, Online, or Offline) and the professional you choose. </p>

    <h3>5. Can I reschedule an appointment?</h3>
    <p>Yes, you can reschedule your appointment. Please visit the "Appointments" section to manage your upcoming sessions.</p>

    <h3>6. What if I miss my appointment?</h3>
    <p>If you miss an appointment, you can contact our support team for assistance in rescheduling it.</p>

    <h3>7. Do I need to create an account to use Calm&Connect?</h3>
    <p>For anonymous consultations, you don't need to create an account. However, creating an account allows you to manage your appointments, access consultation history, and other personalized features.</p>

    <h3>8. Is Calm&Connect available globally?</h3>
    <p>Currently, Calm&Connect is available in select regions. We are working on expanding our services to more areas, so stay tuned for updates!</p>

    <h3>9. How do I contact support?</h3>
    <p>If you need help, you can contact our support team through the "Contact Us" page or via the email provided in the footer of the site.</p>
</div>

